headline: Gen and Vercel Partner to Bring Independent Safety Verification to the AI Skills Ecosystem
summary: As AI agents evolve from assistants into autonomous digital actors capable of executing real-world tasks, Gen (NASDAQ: GEN) today announced a strategic partnership with Vercel to bring independent safety verification to the growing AI skills ecosystem at https://skills.sh/.
